{"tid":2119174,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大物理 你問我答","createTime":"2020-07-22T03:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T07:11:06.000Z","uid":194740,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bfbc919b17345ca380922fc8ff945fa161245daa","tid":2119174,"uid":194740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"恭喜大家終於等到DSE放榜，今年咁樣無論點都好你哋都好叻㗎喇。<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇咩關於CU physics嘅問題想問呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857857ff3f8e28af58adb6bd01604901390f06b9","tid":2119174,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e01480abfc56ca5cfca8cd1b647975fd735081","tid":2119174,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:24:11.000Z","msg":"3字頭科EM難唔難讀？"},{"pid":"6464305c8bd844a8b551bf83d63f374c05d995a0","tid":2119174,"uid":194740,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"857857ff3f8e28af58adb6bd01604901390f06b9","tid":2119174,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"我諗phy會好啲，因為起碼phy係有offer到一個course係專講氣象學（不過都只得1個），但係math就冇喇。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果係想讀氣象學，你想入嘅其實會唔會係earth system science? Physics關於氣象學嘅course得一個咁多，大部分course都唔關事。我建議你去earth system science個website睇吓佢offer嘅course會唔會先係你想要嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n如果學位係ee，我諗應該都得嘅，始終佢個degree requirement有寫engine都得（穩陣啲就打電話/send email去department問），不過master offer嘅course望落同氣象冇乜關係。"},{"pid":"ae7978d900ec409a9eba9cb900619c94c6a05a1d","tid":2119174,"uid":194740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90e01480abfc56ca5cfca8cd1b647975fd735081","tid":2119174,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:24:11.000Z","msg":"3字頭科EM難唔難讀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"呢個見仁見智啦，視乎你讀嘅時候準備成點樣，我就覺得正正常常嘅。<br />\n<br />\n3字頭EM基本上係建基於2字頭嘅EM（introduction) 同2字頭數學course，佢會應用返好多2字頭數學course學過嘅嘢落去。如果之前個底打得好，其實就唔會太難嘅。<br />\n<br />\n佢主要都係講返electrostatics 同magnetostatics。學嘅其實係應用之前學過嘅數學落去EM度，同埋用更多唔同嘅方法嚟solve一個problem，本質上同2字頭其實唔大分別。"},{"pid":"540578567fb5ae97f7251eae168646c09c0bfd3f","tid":2119174,"uid":156335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"之前open day參觀過，見成班人無乜女，入面係咪全男班<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917b9efad70aa28488b5e257f6264dd5f4427017","tid":2119174,"uid":194740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540578567fb5ae97f7251eae168646c09c0bfd3f","tid":2119174,"uid":156335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"之前open day參觀過，見成班人無乜女，入面係咪全男班<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"又唔係全男嘅，都有女，不過同你見到嘅一樣，唔多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab8f2ff4d2fc24b8e8ce31f826386287e0d3b50","tid":2119174,"uid":103362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540578567fb5ae97f7251eae168646c09c0bfd3f","tid":2119174,"uid":156335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"之前open day參觀過，見成班人無乜女，入面係咪全男班<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"我讀個年真係冇咩女仔<br />\n但大學好大, 可以識其他學系"},{"pid":"3b782880e30ef19f2900dea3a7b2178ed4aad73a","tid":2119174,"uid":156335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"917b9efad70aa28488b5e257f6264dd5f4427017","tid":2119174,"uid":194740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"540578567fb5ae97f7251eae168646c09c0bfd3f","tid":2119174,"uid":156335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"之前open day參觀過，見成班人無乜女，入面係咪全男班<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj